This is the repository for the Debathena installer, including the
primary command-line installation script, and PXE installation.

This was split from the "scripts" repository at
fd858268fd08033c74ef9aa533a1e966de38cb15.

Commit IDs referenced in commit messages prior to
dbf5fbd5a8bab9fe74f12de130563959454b9e65 refer to commits in the scripts
repository.

This repository was initialized as follows:
- In a checkout of scripts: git subtree split -P installer -b installer-split
- In this repository: git pull <scripts checkout> installer-split
